---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Docs — PixelPress" description="Quick documentation for running and extending PixelPress.">
  <article class="prose prose-invert max-w-3xl">
    <h1>Docs</h1>
    <h2>Getting started</h2>
    <p>Install dependencies with <code>bun install</code> and run <code>bun run dev</code>.</p>
    <h2>Architecture</h2>
    <p>Marketing pages are Astro routes. The compressor UI lives in a React component mounted only on <code>/app</code>.</p>
    <h2>Privacy</h2>
    <p>Files never leave your device. Compression happens entirely client-side unless future cloud features are explicitly added.</p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
